XirtCMS 2.0 - README
==================================================================================
XirtCMS is an open source content management system that has been developed to 
create online websites and applications with ease. The aim of XirtCMS is to 
provide the community with a flexible Content Management System featuring 
the latest proven technologies.

Name      : XirtCMS
Version   : 2.0
Release   : Q1 2015
Author    : A.G. Gideonse
Copyright : 2010 - 2014, A.G. Gideonse - XirtCMS.com
URLs      : http://www.xirtcms.com

